1) Create a Project Folder
You need a dedicated folder on your computer for this project.
Using File Explorer:

Open File Explorer
Go to your Desktop or Documents
Right click → New → Folder
Name it as you like.

2) Create a Virtual Environment:
Paste in terminal:

python -m venv venv

Now activate it by typing (# On Windows:) :

venv\Scripts\activate

(venv) C:\Users\YourName\Desktop\Folder_name>         (Your terminal should look like this)

Now in the same terminal, copy-paste this and press Enter:

pip install numpy scipy opencv-python matplotlib ipython requests

